def problem(A, K):
    diff_level = 10
    while K >= A[diff_level - 1]:
        K -= A[diff_level - 1]
        A[diff_level - 1] = 0
        diff_level -= 1
    return diff_level
for i in range(int(input())):
    lst = list(map(int, input().split()))
    k = int(input())
    print(problem(lst, k))
